    "prompt": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Which of the following statements correctly describes <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"a sub 1\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"a sub 1\" overflow=\"scroll\"> <msub> <mi>a</mi> <mn>1</mn> </msub> </math></span></span>, and provides a correct justification?</p>\n",
