      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"a sub 1 equals 0\"><math alttext=\"a sub 1 equals 0\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mstyle></math></span></span>, because the can is at the equilibrium position of the can-spring-Earth system.</p>",
